freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: I had a severe autoimmune response with new onset vasculitis like lesions followed by a severe rheumatoid arthritis flare.  They responded after a few days to prednisone.

freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: Biopsy done in rash today, felt possibly autoimmune related and I do have an underlying autoimmune disease.
freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I had a sudden growing rash requiring biopsy today

freetext.HEALTHCARE_VISITS_OTHER: Had very unusual rapid growing lesion, biopsy done 1/15/21.  Suspecting autoimmune process .  Requires topical and systemic pain meds.
